  },
  "*** THANKS TO STRUPPI. JENZ. SOFT SERVE. MOLTARD. AND LUFFAREN ***": {
    "translation": "*** 感谢 Struppi、Jenz、Soft Serve、Moltard 和 Luffaren ***",
